Code organization
--------------------------------------------
/
|
|-doc                                   - documentation
|-img                                   - www - images
|-lib                                   - stylesheet(s)
|-tpl                                   - www templates
|-inc                                   - root for code
    |-modules                           - root for submodules
    |       |-lib                       - module specific handlers
    |
    |-layout                            - layout classes

Configuration
----------------------------------------------

configuration happens through inc/config.py
sample configuration for apache is given in apache.conf
(one might Include apache.conf)

